description: Sometimes two daddies have more in common with each other than a daddy does with one of his young lovers. That’s the situation with Hugh Hunter and Gio Forte, who take a last-minute trip with one another to Fire Island where they have plenty of fun in and out of their swimsuits! The stepsons are left home for this trip — it’s a MEN-only affair!
title: Hugh Hunter And Gio Forte Fuck On Fire Island
